# What is tree shaking ?

Tree shaking is a terminology in which it is not going to load all the code which is not required.
Only required is going to load all other are skipped.

# What is hot module replacement or HMR ?

When application is running and we modified some code and save it.
changes will automatically get reflected into the running application.
Which is called as hot module replacement.

# What is gitignore ?

it contains list of files and direactories that we don't want to commit into the repository

# Why should we not modify package.lock.json ?

It is transitive dependency and installed packages are dependent on this hence it should not modify.
